label: Worcester
description: Shows the topography and geology of Worcester. Mass.

label: Pittsburgh -- Atlantic
description: Cross section of the area between Pittsburgh and the Atlantic Ocean showing cities, geology and topography, together with products manufactured and crops grown in the area.

label: Pittsburgh -- Atlantic
description: Cross section of the area between Pittsburgh and the Atlantic Ocean showing cities, geology and topography, together with products manufactured and crops grown in the area. Shows parts of Delaware.

label: Mexico
description: Cross section of the area in Mexico between Mazatlan to Culiacan in the west, to Brownsville and Matamoros in the east. Shows cities, geology, agricultural products and industries of the area.

label: England
description: Cross section of the area between Dublin and Wicklow Mountains in Ireland and the Norfolk Broads in England. Shows cities, geology, topography of the area and agricultural products of Ireland.

label: From Lubeck to Milan (Baltic to the Dolomites)
description: Cross section of the area in Europe from Lübeck, Germany, in the north to the Valley of the Po River, Italy, in the south. Shows geology, topography, and cities of the area.

label: Adriatic -- Baltic
description: Cross section of a part of Eastern Europe and the Balkan Peninsula, from Kaliningrad in the north to Dubrovnik in the south. Shows landforms, geology, cities, mineral resources, agricultural products and industries of the area.

label: Tibet -- Central Asia
description: Cross section of the area in Asia starting with Chittagong and Dhaka in the south to Stalinsk [Novokuznetsk, Sakha (Russian Federation)] in the north. Shows cities, geology, topography, agricultural products and industries of the area.

label: From Black Sea thru Turkey to Cyprus
description: Cross section of the area between Kastamonu İli (Turkey) in the north to Limassol (Cyprus) in the south. Shows cities, geology and topography, natural resources and crops grown in the area depicted.

label: Australia
description: Cross section of the area of Australia between Perth and Freemantle on the Indian Ocean to Sydney and Newcastle in the East. Shows cities, geology and topography, agricultural products and mineral resources.

label: General landscape
description: Cross section of a general landscape showing topography.

label: Sable Island -- Fredewricton N.B.
description: Cross section of the area between Sable Island, N.S. through Halifax Region N.S. to Fredericton, N.B.; showing cities, geology and topography, and industries, agricultural crops and fisheries in the area depicted.

label: Mount Tremblant -- Catskills
description: Cross section of the Greater Antilles from Jamaica in the South to Bahamas in the North. Shows geology and topography of the area.

label: Jamaica - Bahamas : unfinished
description: Cross section of the Greater Antilles from Jamaica in the South to Bahamas in the North. Shows geology and topography of the area.

label: Santiago -- Buenos Aires
description: Cross section of the area between Santiago de Chile and Buenos Aires showing cities, geology and topography, climate and crops grown in the area depicted.

label: China, north - south
description: Cross section of China from Beijing and Dalian in the North to the island of Taiwan in the South. Shows cities, geology, topography, agricultural products and industries of the area.

label: South Africa
description: Cross section of the area in the Republic of South Africa between CapeTown and Cape of Good Hope in the West and the Pietermaritzburg in The North and Durban in the East. Shows also a crossection of a part of Basutoland. Shows cities, geology, agricultural products of the area.
